My Background

I'm Mahdi, a 23-year-old self-taught programmer from Iran who discovered his passion for coding in 2021. My journey began with C++, and I quickly fell in love with its complexity. However, my hunger for knowledge led me to explore both Frontend and Backend development, aspiring to become a full-stack developer by the most famous full-stack development course in Udemy.
